of all the coolest-side of core meets BIG creative institutions built in our generation @NikeSB has always struck the chord with me the most. from day 0 to what they have built now deserves the biggest round of applause. bless Sandy Bodecker and his vision. the genre of film that is a @nike commercial itself is another important tradition to continue. on that note, one time for all the artists and athletes involved in our new @Off____White™ c/o @Nike bag...

an @arch___itecture film overseen by @chloe.actually @mahfuzsultan

written & directed by~
@JulianKlincewicz simulationdiary @wordsplayed @swishprojects

starring~
kevin bradley #kevinbradley

more in the 𝓛𝓸𝓾𝓲𝓼 door, 3 poignant ones; @ibkamara, @shaynehba + @anonymousclub.club, Olu Odukoya @modernmattermagazine @omo.inc 

again, it’s been the same ethos since i started. keep the doors open that i walk thru as it’s the logic i believe in the most. nothing is as reassuring as this slideshow above. i’m so particular that it’s vital there’s physical artifacts of wide sweeping ideas or it doesn’t count in my book. 

please find the work of the multitude of artists i value from my specific corner of the world. each given free reign to bounce ideas off the @louisvuitton seat i sit at. follow them and dive into their premise. to be continued... #louis200
